# KitfoxPay — 唯一需要的环境变量 / The only environment variable needed
#
# 所有其他配置（Jeepay、Paystack、服务器、管理密码等）通过管理界面设置：
# All other config (Jeepay, Paystack, server, admin password, etc.) is set via admin UI:
#   http://your-domain:9219
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DATABASE_URL — PostgreSQL 连接字符串 / PostgreSQL connection string
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 作用 / What it does:
#   1. 配置持久化：管理界面保存的所有配置存入数据库
#      Config persistence: all config saved via admin UI is stored in DB
#      重启、重部署后自动从数据库恢复，无需重新配置
#      Auto-restored from DB on restart/redeploy — no reconfiguration needed
#
#   2. Webhook 幂等性：防止同一支付通知被重复处理
#      Webhook idempotency: prevents duplicate payment processing across restarts
#
# 不设置 → 内存模式（功能完整，但重部署后需重新配置管理界面）
# Not set → memory mode (fully functional, but admin config lost on redeploy)
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 兼容任何 PostgreSQL 提供商 / Works with any PostgreSQL provider:
#
#   Supabase  → Dashboard → Project Settings → Database → Connection String → URI
#   Aiven     → Service Overview → Connection Information → Service URI
#   Neon      → Dashboard → Connection Details → Connection string
#   Railway   → Service → Variables → DATABASE_URL (auto-injected)
#   本地      → postgresql://user:password@localhost:5432/kitfoxpay
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#
# 在 Render 上设置 / Setting on Render:
#   Dashboard → Your Service → Environment → Add Environment Variable
#   Key:   DATABASE_URL
#   Value: (粘贴连接字符串 / paste your connection string)
#
# 首次启动自动建表，无需手动执行任何 SQL。
# Tables are created automatically on first run — no manual SQL needed.

DATABASE_URL=postgresql://user:password@host:5432/dbname

# HF Spaces 专用（可选）/ HF Spaces only (optional):
# HF Spaces 固定使用 7860 端口 / HF Spaces requires port 7860
# SERVER_PORT=7860
